  "script_model_response": "Now I have all the data needed. Let me analyze the historical data to find the highest closing price.\n\nFrom the historical data (2024-01-01 to 2024-04-30), I need to identify the day with the highest closing price:\n\nLooking through the data:\n- **March 8, 2024**: Close $97.40 (this was the high, not close)\n- **March 25, 2024**: Close $95.00\n- **March 26, 2024**: Close $92.56\n- **March 22, 2024**: Close $94.29\n\nLet me find the actual highest close - scanning through:\n- **March 8, 2024**: Close = $87.528\n- **March 25, 2024**: Close = $95.00\n- **March 26, 2024**: Close = $92.56\n\nThe highest closing price was on **March 25, 2024** at **$95.00** (specifically $95.0019989).\n\n---\n\n## NVIDIA (NVDA) Stock Analysis Results\n\n### 1. Historical High-Close Day (Jan 1 - Apr 30, 2024)\n- **Date:** March 25, 2024\n- **Closing Price:** $95.00\n\n### 2. Current Real-Time Price\n- **Current Price:** $198.45\n- **Date:** May 1, 2026\n\n### 3. Percentage Difference Calculation\n\n**Formula:** ((Current Price - Historical High Close) / Historical High Close) × 100\n\n**Calculation:** (($198.45 - $95.00) / $95.00) × 100 = **108.89%**\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Historical High-Close Date | March 25, 2024 |\n| Historical High-Close Price | $95.00 |\n| Current Real-Time Price | $198.45 |\n| **Percentage Increase** | **+108.89%** |\n\nNVIDIA's stock price has more than doubled since its highest closing price in the January-April 2024 period, representing a remarkable **108.89% increase** from that historical high-close of $95.00 to today's price of $198.45.",
